15
00:01:12,360 --> 00:01:16,300
 ♫ Falling into endless love ♫ 

16
00:01:16,300 --> 00:01:19,420
 ♫ Stirring waves upending a lifetime ♫ 

17
00:01:19,420 --> 00:01:22,760
 ♫ Even if this life leads to ruin ♫ 

18
00:01:22,760 --> 00:01:27,020
 ♫ I still choose to be entangled with you ♫ 

19
00:01:27,020 --> 00:01:30,225
 ♫ Through all lifetimes ♫ 

20
00:01:30,225 --> 00:01:36,620
 

21
00:01:36,620 --> 00:01:39,500
 

22
00:01:42,540 --> 00:01:46,120
 I heard they vanished here. 

23
00:02:05,750 --> 00:02:07,670
 So much blood was spilled. 

24
00:02:07,670 --> 00:02:10,960
 Seems like Sima Jiao is severely hurt. 

25
00:02:10,960 --> 00:02:13,610
Master Yuan, there are bloodstains here.

26
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:16,400
Let's follow the blood trail.

27
00:02:23,320 --> 00:02:25,490
They came here, too.

28
00:02:25,490 --> 00:02:28,220
The blood suddenly vanishes here.

29
00:02:28,220 --> 00:02:29,820
How strange.

30
00:02:29,820 --> 00:02:34,810
Looks like we can no longer track
Sima Jiao's whereabouts.

31
00:02:34,810 --> 00:02:37,270
He must have used some secret spell.

32
00:02:37,270 --> 00:02:39,480
We must search harder.

33
00:02:39,480 --> 00:02:42,450
Sima Jiao slaughtered countless innocents

34
00:02:42,450 --> 00:02:44,520
at Chiyan City and Baifeng Mountain.

35
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:46,610
If we don't seal him now,

36
00:02:46,610 --> 00:02:50,000
he will massacre again when he recovers.

37
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:53,670
Indeed, but staying here is pointless.

38
00:02:53,670 --> 00:02:58,020
I think we should return and discuss with the other palace heads.

39
00:02:58,020 --> 00:02:59,540
Let's go.

40
00:03:08,990 --> 00:03:11,920
 Using Ting Yan's extreme-cold nature
is hopeless. 

41
00:03:11,920 --> 00:03:13,990
 I can't take her core and harm her. 

42
00:03:13,990 --> 00:03:15,870
 To break the Immortal-Demon Barrier, 

43
00:03:15,870 --> 00:03:17,670
 there's only one way left. 

44
00:03:17,670 --> 00:03:19,920
 Killing Sima Jiao. 

45
00:03:19,920 --> 00:03:22,430
 When the Spirit Fire dies, the barrier breaks. 

46
00:03:22,430 --> 00:03:23,710
 He was too strong before. 

47
00:03:23,710 --> 00:03:25,240
 I couldn't strike. 

48
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:28,660
 Now, he's gravely wounded and alone. 

49
00:03:28,660 --> 00:03:33,030
 If I find allies, I may succeed. 

50
00:03:42,240 --> 00:03:45,650
- What are you afraid of?
- You tell me.

51
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:50,040
Grandmaster, spare me.

52
00:03:50,040 --> 00:03:51,430
I can't take it anymore.

53
00:03:51,430 --> 00:03:53,020
No mercy.

54
00:03:53,870 --> 00:03:55,270
What?

55
00:03:55,270 --> 00:03:57,040
You dislike it?

56
00:04:00,150 --> 00:04:01,900
I dislike it.

57
00:04:04,360 --> 00:04:07,920
Looks like you're indeed severely hurt.

58
00:04:07,920 --> 00:04:10,880
Even the Truth Spell failed.

59
00:04:14,830 --> 00:04:16,750
You said...

60
00:04:17,680 --> 00:04:19,520
you dislike it.

61
00:04:20,150 --> 00:04:22,670
Do you actually like it?

62
00:04:23,520 --> 00:04:26,080
 Why force me to speak the truth? 

63
00:04:26,080 --> 00:04:29,710
 There are many ways
to know what a person truly feels. 

64
00:04:29,710 --> 00:04:31,760
Without the Truth Spell,

65
00:04:32,350 --> 00:04:37,370
I can still sense
if you speak the truth or not.

66
00:04:37,880 --> 00:04:41,170
 What's with this atmosphere? 

67
00:04:41,170 --> 00:04:45,350
 Looks like that little flame was right. 

68
00:04:45,350 --> 00:04:49,670
 Sima Jiao truly likes me. 

69
00:04:52,790 --> 00:04:53,860
Serene Vale's specialty.

70
00:04:53,860 --> 00:04:56,840
It clears the mind. Try it.

71
00:05:07,080 --> 00:05:10,420
He hardly seems injured.

72
00:05:11,320 --> 00:05:14,120
This place is the Mindscape
that person created.

73
00:05:14,120 --> 00:05:15,760
In half a day,

74
00:05:16,320 --> 00:05:18,200
it will vanish.

75
00:05:19,520 --> 00:05:22,200
No wonder it never turns dark.

76
00:05:22,200 --> 00:05:24,210
There are no pursuers either.

77
00:05:25,080 --> 00:05:29,030
By the way, that master asked me to tell you

78
00:05:29,030 --> 00:05:32,000
that other Spirit Fire still exists.

79
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:33,760
What does that mean?

80
00:05:33,760 --> 00:05:37,560
The Spirit Fire that
Shi Qian Lv secretly raised

81
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:39,030
likely hasn't gone out.

82
00:05:39,030 --> 00:05:41,790
Why did Shi Qian Lv raise it secretly?

83
00:05:41,790 --> 00:05:44,880
Isn't the Spirit Fire only for the Sima clan?

84
00:05:44,880 --> 00:05:49,370
Do you know that the Sima clan once ascended?

85
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:51,880
It was recorded in Gengchen's history.

86
00:05:51,880 --> 00:05:55,520
Years ago, many powerful Sima cultivators

87
00:05:55,520 --> 00:05:58,640
ascended to immortality through tribulation.

88
00:06:00,080 --> 00:06:04,680
Ascending to immortality is just a joke.

89
00:06:04,680 --> 00:06:08,150
Whenever an immortal ascended in the past,

90
00:06:08,150 --> 00:06:11,350
the world brimmed with spiritual energy.

91
00:06:11,350 --> 00:06:12,390
That I know.

92
00:06:12,390 --> 00:06:16,200
Books say when immortals ascend,

93
00:06:16,200 --> 00:06:18,390
the gate to the divine opens,

94
00:06:18,390 --> 00:06:20,720
and spiritual energy
flows into the mortal realm.

95
00:06:21,270 --> 00:06:24,960
The truth is that those immortals

96
00:06:24,960 --> 00:06:27,590
never reached the divine world.

97
00:06:27,590 --> 00:06:30,170
They dissolved into the world.

98
00:06:30,170 --> 00:06:33,640
Their souls and flesh
became pure spiritual energy

99
00:06:33,640 --> 00:06:36,030
and returned to the world.

100
00:06:36,030 --> 00:06:40,710
Now, the Sima clan is near extinction.

101
00:06:40,710 --> 00:06:43,980
It is fate within the heavens

102
00:06:44,830 --> 00:06:46,840
that wants to destroy the Sima clan.

103
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:51,710
No wonder the Eight Palaces
and the Shi family

104
00:06:51,710 --> 00:06:54,640
dared to scheme against
the last of the Sima clan.

105
00:06:54,640 --> 00:06:56,550
- It's because they know...
- They know

106
00:06:56,550 --> 00:07:01,490
the glory of ascension was fake.

107
00:07:02,640 --> 00:07:05,470
Except for the Sima clan,

108
00:07:05,470 --> 00:07:09,320
no one knows the way to end the curse

109
00:07:09,320 --> 00:07:11,520
is by merging with the Spirit Fire.

110
00:07:13,350 --> 00:07:16,670
And you just revealed this secret to me?

111
00:07:17,760 --> 00:07:19,880
I don't need to hide anything from you.

112
00:07:22,640 --> 00:07:27,680
It seems Shi Qian Lv has learned
this secret that bred his greed.

113
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:30,560
That's why he raised the Spirit Fire
to gain eternal life.

114
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:32,520
- Right?
- Yes.

115
00:07:32,520 --> 00:07:34,470
He created Baifeng Mountain

116
00:07:34,470 --> 00:07:38,830
to seize Fengshan blood
by a blood-swapping ritual.

117
00:07:38,830 --> 00:07:41,640
That way, he could merge with the Spirit Fire.

118
00:07:41,640 --> 00:07:45,000
But I've destroyed Baifeng Mountain.

119
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:47,270
He probably can't sustain Spirit Fire.

120
00:07:47,270 --> 00:07:49,580
But that old man said so.

121
00:07:49,580 --> 00:07:51,730
Shi Qian Lv's Spirit Fire still burns.

122
00:07:51,730 --> 00:07:55,540
It means he hid
the Fengshan bloodline elsewhere.

123
00:07:55,540 --> 00:07:58,230
Blood-swapping for eternal life?

124
00:07:58,230 --> 00:08:01,390
Shi Qian Lv is bold indeed.

125
00:08:01,390 --> 00:08:05,640
Do you plan to kill him?

126
00:08:05,640 --> 00:08:08,110
Killing him alone won't do.

127
00:08:08,910 --> 00:08:13,320
I will plant hidden fires
in the nine spiritual peaks that nourish the Shi family.

128
00:08:13,320 --> 00:08:16,440
When I find Shi Qian Lv's Spirit Fire,

129
00:08:16,440 --> 00:08:19,830
I will ignite the fuse of the spiritual peaks

130
00:08:19,830 --> 00:08:24,030
and ruin the Shi family's century-old delusion.

131
00:08:24,030 --> 00:08:26,570
But you just woke up.

132
00:08:27,340 --> 00:08:30,250
How about you get better first?

133
00:08:30,250 --> 00:08:31,890
I don't know medicine.

134
00:08:31,890 --> 00:08:35,080
If you collapse again,
what if I can't save you?

135
00:08:35,080 --> 00:08:36,460
It doesn't matter.

136
00:08:36,460 --> 00:08:40,470
I have many ways to ruin the Shi family.

137
00:08:42,750 --> 00:08:44,730
As long as I don't wish it,

138
00:08:44,730 --> 00:08:47,060
no one can kill me.

139
00:08:48,280 --> 00:08:51,980
Then do you still want to die?

140
00:08:56,710 --> 00:09:01,070
You tried so hard to save me,
so I'll stay alive.

141
00:09:05,750 --> 00:09:07,980
Where do we go next?

142
00:09:07,980 --> 00:09:10,280
We'll go to the Shi family.

143
00:09:28,630 --> 00:09:30,460
Madam Ye.

144
00:09:33,350 --> 00:09:37,650
Madam Ye, what brings you here?

145
00:09:37,650 --> 00:09:42,460
I came to ask what you will do with Sima Jiao

146
00:09:42,460 --> 00:09:45,340
if you find him.

147
00:09:46,040 --> 00:09:50,400
I will once again seal him
in Three Saints Mountain.

148
00:09:50,400 --> 00:09:57,090
We need you to help us
in activating the sealing array.

149
00:10:00,750 --> 00:10:02,610
Sect Master Shi.

150
00:10:03,320 --> 00:10:06,970
You probably have other plans.

151
00:10:10,750 --> 00:10:13,110
Why do you say this?

152
00:10:13,110 --> 00:10:17,510
Baifeng Mountain was your work.

153
00:10:17,510 --> 00:10:22,590
I wonder where all the Fengshan blood

154
00:10:22,590 --> 00:10:25,090
in the mountain went?

155
00:10:25,960 --> 00:10:28,470
I wonder, too.

156
00:10:29,080 --> 00:10:33,630
Instead of telling these to other palace heads,

157
00:10:33,630 --> 00:10:36,370
why come to me?

158
00:10:36,370 --> 00:10:38,490
What do you seek?

159
00:10:41,800 --> 00:10:44,360
I want Sima Jiao's life.

160
00:10:48,160 --> 00:10:54,970
I never thought you hated Sima Jiao this much.

161
00:10:56,110 --> 00:11:01,430
But your actions aren't for private revenge.

162
00:11:01,430 --> 00:11:06,870
It's to break the Immortal-Demon Barrier.

163
00:11:06,870 --> 00:11:08,990
We both have secrets.

164
00:11:08,990 --> 00:11:11,200
No need to hide.

165
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:13,690
I'll only ask you one thing.

166
00:11:14,560 --> 00:11:17,360
Do you mean to kill Sima Jiao?

167
00:11:20,960 --> 00:11:23,440
I can work with you.

168
00:11:23,440 --> 00:11:25,630
Whether it's to kill a person
or to put out the fire.

169
00:11:25,630 --> 00:11:31,780
But what do I gain from doing this?

170
00:11:32,510 --> 00:11:36,750
I'll keep matters
on Baifeng Mountain confidential.

171
00:11:36,750 --> 00:11:38,710
That's what you gain.

172
00:11:47,560 --> 00:11:49,320
Madam Ye.

173
00:11:49,320 --> 00:11:53,110
I have plenty of ways to shut you up.

174
00:11:53,110 --> 00:11:57,110
What use is any of this to me?

175
00:12:06,990 --> 00:12:08,590
Don't forget.

176
00:12:08,590 --> 00:12:11,590
My cultivation isn't as strong as yours,

177
00:12:11,590 --> 00:12:13,830
but I'm the mistress of a palace after all.

178
00:12:13,830 --> 00:12:18,710
I hope you won't underestimate me.

179
00:12:18,710 --> 00:12:22,370
But you and I share the same goal,

180
00:12:22,370 --> 00:12:25,230
so why waste effort working against each other?

181
00:12:25,230 --> 00:12:26,960
Why don't we join forces?

182
00:12:27,590 --> 00:12:31,610
After it's done, we each take what we need.

183
00:12:33,400 --> 00:12:37,940
I greatly admire your boldness.

184
00:12:39,560 --> 00:12:44,110
I also hope you'll let me know

185
00:12:44,110 --> 00:12:46,320
as soon as you have news.

186
00:12:46,320 --> 00:12:50,120
I also hope you'll keep your word.

187
00:12:58,870 --> 00:13:00,590
Greetings, Aunt.

188
00:13:00,590 --> 00:13:03,080
Xu, no need for such formalities.

189
00:13:03,080 --> 00:13:04,920
I was incompetent.

190
00:13:04,920 --> 00:13:06,400
I disappointed Father.

191
00:13:06,400 --> 00:13:08,040
That's why I disturbed you, Aunt.

192
00:13:08,040 --> 00:13:09,630
It's fine.
 

193
00:13:09,630 --> 00:13:13,400
I entered seclusion to improve my cultivation

194
00:13:13,400 --> 00:13:16,160
so that I can help your father.

195
00:13:16,160 --> 00:13:20,510
Capturing Sima Jiao as soon as possible is the top priority.

196
00:13:21,280 --> 00:13:24,870
The destruction of Baifeng Mountain
isn't your fault.

197
00:13:24,870 --> 00:13:27,830
You don't need to blame yourself too much.

198
00:13:27,830 --> 00:13:29,690
Thank you, Aunt.

199
00:13:31,560 --> 00:13:33,830
All disciples, heed my command.

200
00:13:33,830 --> 00:13:36,710
Split into two groups
and follow me and your young master

201
00:13:36,710 --> 00:13:38,590
to search for Sima Jiao.

202
00:13:38,590 --> 00:13:40,260
 Yes. 

203
00:13:40,260 --> 00:13:43,166
 

204
00:13:48,470 --> 00:13:50,010
Grandmaster.

205
00:13:50,710 --> 00:13:52,510
Sima Jiao.

206
00:13:52,510 --> 00:13:56,600
Why can't these people see us and why don't they run into us?

207
00:13:56,600 --> 00:13:59,040
I concealed us with invisibility.

208
00:13:59,040 --> 00:14:01,100
These people are low in cultivation.

209
00:14:01,800 --> 00:14:05,510
If they feel a strong aura, they will avoid it on their own.

210
00:14:09,110 --> 00:14:10,320
It still works even when you're injured?

211
00:14:10,320 --> 00:14:12,110
Even if my serious injuries haven't healed,

212
00:14:12,110 --> 00:14:15,840
these people are far from my match.

213
00:14:16,510 --> 00:14:19,510
Why don't we just use
the invisibility all the time?

214
00:14:20,040 --> 00:14:23,830
Invisibility consumes
quite a lot of spiritual power.

215
00:14:23,830 --> 00:14:26,440
I can only maintain it for a brief moment.

216
00:14:26,440 --> 00:14:27,990
Right.

217
00:14:27,990 --> 00:14:29,990
You're still badly injured.

218
00:14:29,990 --> 00:14:32,830
Various high-level spells have failed, too.

219
00:14:32,830 --> 00:14:34,870
Let's keep a low profile.

220
00:14:34,870 --> 00:14:37,870
After all, we're on the run, not on vacation.

221
00:14:42,440 --> 00:14:45,350
You don't need to worry about these things.

222
00:14:45,350 --> 00:14:47,160
With me here,

223
00:14:47,160 --> 00:14:49,280
wherever you go is a vacation.

224
00:14:50,870 --> 00:14:53,260
That's a bold statement.

225
00:14:55,200 --> 00:14:59,200
By the way, where are we?

226
00:14:59,200 --> 00:15:03,110
It feels more and more remote on the way here.

227
00:15:03,110 --> 00:15:04,920
Luo River Immortal District.

228
00:15:04,920 --> 00:15:08,800
A district where ordinary people
and cultivators live side by side.

229
00:15:09,510 --> 00:15:12,200
It's the most marginal area
of Gengchen Celestial Palace.

230
00:15:12,200 --> 00:15:15,800
No wonder these people look like they don't know any spells.

231
00:15:15,800 --> 00:15:18,040
There are few cultivators, too.

232
00:15:18,040 --> 00:15:20,110
It seems more like a place where mortals live.

233
00:15:20,110 --> 00:15:25,050
They're only ostracized people or low-level cultivators.

234
00:15:28,630 --> 00:15:32,590
So, does that make me a big shot here?

235
00:15:33,350 --> 00:15:36,460
You've already reached late Soulshift.

236
00:15:36,460 --> 00:15:40,080
You're only one step away
from entering Void Forge.

237
00:15:40,080 --> 00:15:42,040
What a dump.

238
00:15:42,590 --> 00:15:44,110
Be careful.
 

239
00:15:44,110 --> 00:15:45,830
If you break my things,
 

240
00:15:45,830 --> 00:15:47,710
I'll take your lives.

241
00:15:58,350 --> 00:16:00,110
What a display.

242
00:16:00,110 --> 00:16:02,660
Who were those two just now?

243
00:16:09,400 --> 00:16:11,110
- Have you seen this person?
- No.

244
00:16:11,110 --> 00:16:12,780
Have you seen this person?

245
00:16:13,470 --> 00:16:15,080
- Have you seen this person?
- Out of the way!

246
00:16:15,080 --> 00:16:16,200
Have you seen him or not? Look carefully.

247
00:16:16,200 --> 00:16:17,680
- Have you seen him?
- I don't know him.

248
00:16:17,680 --> 00:16:19,290
Have you seen this person?

249
00:16:21,350 --> 00:16:22,920
- Have you seen this person?
- Sima Jiao!

250
00:16:22,920 --> 00:16:25,100
Hurry, they're up there!

251
00:16:33,280 --> 00:16:34,700
- You two, go that way. 
 - Okay.

252
00:16:34,700 --> 00:16:36,530
- The rest, follow me. 
 - Yes.

253
00:16:48,510 --> 00:16:49,940
This way!

254
00:17:15,360 --> 00:17:17,110
Who are you?

255
00:17:22,360 --> 00:17:25,520
Did someone else come in just now?

256
00:17:26,550 --> 00:17:28,750
Are you all blind?

257
00:17:28,750 --> 00:17:35,840
Or is this your room
and we Mu siblings should give way to you?

258
00:17:35,840 --> 00:17:39,470
Senior Aunt, there are rumors that Master Mu's grandchildren

259
00:17:39,470 --> 00:17:41,580
are coming here to study.

260
00:17:42,270 --> 00:17:46,130
They're just nobodies who are clinging to the Shi family.

261
00:17:47,230 --> 00:17:48,620
Let's go.

262
00:17:57,440 --> 00:17:59,150
You can play with this.

263
00:18:00,510 --> 00:18:04,750
So, these are the arrogant siblings?

264
00:18:05,790 --> 00:18:07,190
Yes.

265
00:18:08,070 --> 00:18:11,680
Weren't we going to
take revenge on Shi Qian Lv?

